We may modify our Privacy Policy for various reasons such as to improve our Services, to reflect our Services offered on our website, in the Application or Apps, and/or to comply with relevant laws. We encourage you to stay up-to-date and review these changes. If you wish to discontinue using our Service, the Application, website or Apps, please contact us or alternatively close your
